@DATABASE "Soul Of A Robot"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Soul Of A Robot"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                              Soul Of A Robot
                              ===============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(25812,255)"}               25812,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Multi-POKE     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(25816,0)"}               25816,0

                         The Multi-POKE gives you 55 lives, 5500 psyche &
                         a laser.


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
